h3-manage-prepaid-plans-android.translation:
### 管理预付费方案（Android） \{#manage-prepaid-plans-android\}

如果您的应用用户可以购买[预付费方案](https://developer.android.com/google/play/billing/subscriptions#prepaid-plans)（例如，购买数月的非续订订阅），您可以为预付费方案启用[待处理交易](https://developer.android.com/google/play/billing/subscriptions#pending)。

```dart showLineNumbers title="main.dart"
await Adapty().activate(
  configuration: AdaptyConfiguration(apiKey: 'YOUR_PUBLIC_SDK_KEY')
    ..withGoogleEnablePendingPrepaidPlans(true),
);
```
